query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_lenders,
  COUNT(url) as with_url,
  COUNT(phone) as with_phone,
  COUNT(CASE WHEN url IS NOT NULL AND url != '' THEN 1 END) as with_nonempty_url
FROM lenders;
SELECT name, url, phone FROM lenders LIMIT 5;
